metadata.name: A sofa in the woods?
metadata.description:
As I ventured along the woodland path, an unsettling sensation crept over me, as if unseen eyes were fixed upon my every step. 
And then, emerging from the trees, stood an ancient and dilapidated couch, its decaying form etching an indelible mark upon my consciousness. 
A compulsion welled within me, urging me to immortalize this haunting sight through the lens.
